msgstr "エラー報告に関するガイドライン"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/whisperback/whisperback.ui.in:445
msgid ""
"<b>Email address</b>\n"
"So we can answer you or ask for more details."
msgstr ""
"<b>メールアドレス</b>\n"
"ご回答または詳細をお伺いいたします。"

#: ../config/chroot_local-includes/usr/share/whisperback/whisperback.ui.in:480
